An off duty cop shot and killed two men who attempted to
hijack his car in Kwazulu-Natal.The cop was driving his vehicle along Dazi Meyiwa Road,
Section 10, KwaMakhutha, when the incident occurred on Monday.The two armed men were driving in a stolen white
